Package models

Class Summary
DataPublisher The DataPublisher class is related to the MongoDB DataPublisher collection created after the harvesting process (gbiffrance-harvest)
Dataset The Dataset class is related to the MongoDB Dataset collection created after the harvesting process (gbiffrance-harvest)
Occurrence The Occurrence class is related to the ElasticSearch collection created after the harvesting process (gbiffrance-harvest)
Place the Place class is used to stored the information coming from the Yahoo Geo! web service (http://where.yahooapis.com)
Search The Search class is used to generate a taxe/place/dataset/date search
Taxa the Taxa class is used to stored the information coming from the ECAT web service (http://ecat-dev.gbif.org/) and EOL webservice
Util The Util class gathers diverse useful methods
